episodes.title: Rep. Nancy Mace wants more from the Department of Justice after viewing unredacted Epstein files
episodes.description:
CHARLESTON, S.C. (WCIV) — U.S. Rep. Nancy Mace didn't mince words Thursday after viewing portions of the unredacted files related to the investigation into Jeffrey Epstein. She wants the Department of Justice to do more.

READ MORE: https://abcnews4.com/news/lowcountry-and-state-politics/rep-mace-presses-doj-for-more-action-after-viewing-unredacted-epstein-files
